Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.70,0:00:16.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(拍攝地點  宇宙)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.11,0:00:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,銀河天使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.25,0:00:31.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(大家跟著一起唱吧)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.22,0:00:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓你久等了  Everybody
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.39,0:00:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,HIGH  就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.89,0:00:37.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總是精神緊繃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.06,0:00:42.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論是波奇、老闆\N帥哥或是上校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.56,0:00:43.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都很棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.06,0:00:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,假日上街買東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.07,0:00:50.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吃到美味的試吃品  Lucky
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.74,0:00:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果想預約申請約會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.07,0:00:56.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隨時接受登記
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.41,0:01:00.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果想談戀愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.75,0:01:03.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能只是一昧地追求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.75,0:01:08.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剩下就得靠神明幫忙保佑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.42,0:01:11.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一切皆微笑以對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.09,0:01:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來，笑一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:12.59,0:01:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,充滿夢想的天使隊  Guu
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.76,0:01:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,輕輕鬆鬆毫不在乎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.60,0:01:18.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一切都打平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.93,0:01:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凡事付之一笑  WAHAHA
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.10,0:01:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要吃幾碗請自便
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.94,0:01:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吃到飽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.27,0:01:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,願望是郊遊旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.61,0:01:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,狼吞虎嚥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.44,0:01:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,話題沸騰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.28,0:01:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,超人氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.61,0:01:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,包在我們身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.78,0:01:37.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,熊、熊、熊貓\N熊、熊、熊貓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.78,0:01:41.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,熊、熊、熊貓\N熊、熊、熊貓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.45,0:01:44.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來分個黑白是非吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.29,0:01:46.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一切皆微笑以對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.56,0:01:52.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(火藥味與煙草味的摩擦)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.53,0:01:59.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使還是老樣子\N空蕩蕩的什麼都沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.24,0:02:01.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好歹也準備個房間的主人嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.48,0:02:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兩年沒見面了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.02,0:02:19.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,假裝咳了一次咳嗽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.96,0:02:21.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後只再敲一次門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.70,0:02:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的好閒呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.63,0:02:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯嗯，偶而悠閒地休息也不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.91,0:02:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,饒了我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.41,0:02:38.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,耳際一邊聽著青春腐爛的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.21,0:02:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要我如何悠閒地休息啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.94,0:02:43.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早知道會這樣的話\N我也去請年假就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.15,0:02:44.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,年假？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.38,0:02:45.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.75,0:02:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天一早突然請了年假呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.82,0:02:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大概是去約會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.32,0:02:51.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳說什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.79,0:02:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,昨天有個男人打電話找佛特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.83,0:02:57.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說要在房間等她之類的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.50,0:03:00.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有啦\N我絕對沒有偷聽她講電話喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.07,0:03:02.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真羨慕佛特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.40,0:03:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼好羨慕的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.00,0:03:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把我這個死黨\N獨自丟在不毛的沙漠不管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.71,0:03:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,男人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.74,0:03:10.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她什麼時候有的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.94,0:03:11.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.41,0:03:15.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去外面巡邏囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.78,0:03:17.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼要我去？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.12,0:03:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當領航員啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.18,0:03:19.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.88,0:03:20.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.35,0:03:22.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然只想自己一個人幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.09,0:03:23.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我絕不讓妳如願\N神明保佑…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.49,0:03:25.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，佛特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.06,0:03:27.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳有在聽嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.36,0:03:28.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.73,0:03:33.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼回自己房間\N還得被關在外面啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.07,0:03:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿健\N你要抱怨的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.30,0:03:39.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就抱怨自己的粗心大意吧\N不鎖門就跑出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.44,0:03:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳這是什麼話啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.94,0:03:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是去樓下的商店\N買些喝的東西而已耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.48,0:03:48.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,寒酸的男人房間\N加上廉價酒的酒宴是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.78,0:03:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用這來招待突然找出來的女人\N未免太隆重了點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.22,0:03:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳說話還是一樣的苛刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.29,0:03:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.39,0:03:57.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳就是這一點…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.09,0:04:00.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吸引我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.26,0:04:05.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有點…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.03,0:04:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,離題了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.47,0:04:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香煙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.84,0:04:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不是戒掉了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.81,0:04:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最近開始重視身體健康
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.97,0:04:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,盡量不給自己多餘的壓力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.01,0:04:20.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,工作呢？\N有繼續在做嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.01,0:04:23.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯，託妳的福\N還有繼續在做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.75,0:04:24.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別看我這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.35,0:04:27.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在士官學校的成績\N可是第一名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.65,0:04:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以還不缺委託上門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.19,0:04:32.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真令人懷念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.99,0:04:36.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那段在士官學校\N彼此較勁技術的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.03,0:04:41.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那時候妳的夢想是加入軍隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.77,0:04:43.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.37,0:04:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果沒發生那個事件\N就不會離開學校…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.31,0:04:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，是我，妳現在在哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.42,0:04:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這樣子的，我們溜出來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.68,0:05:01.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果方便的話\N要不要跟我們會合…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.65,0:05:02.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,掛斷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.29,0:05:04.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是當然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.46,0:05:06.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在她正忙著呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.92,0:05:09.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別說廢話\N立刻給我進行訊源追蹤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.46,0:05:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,訊源追蹤？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.53,0:05:13.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不然你以為我幹嘛帶你出來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.13,0:05:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是，為什麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.57,0:05:17.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想被扔出車外\N自己回去嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.60,0:05:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給我10秒鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.30,0:05:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後去了要做什麼呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.21,0:05:23.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要給佛特一點顏色瞧瞧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.47,0:05:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人生不如意之事十之八九
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.18,0:05:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後呢，你想要說什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.48,0:05:32.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.08,0:05:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要抽煙！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.12,0:05:36.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不是答應過我了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.42,0:05:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自從那事件以後\N你的肺…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.82,0:05:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,約定是嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.49,0:05:44.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實我是想問問妳的意見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.30,0:05:47.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也會聽別人的意見？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.63,0:05:51.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真想讓那些被你搞得頭大的\N教官們聽聽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.80,0:05:54.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吧，我就聽你說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.47,0:05:55.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.88,0:06:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,訊源在前面的貧民街
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.08,0:06:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,貧民街…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.35,0:06:04.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,光聽這個名詞\N似乎就感覺有股危險男人的香味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.58,0:06:08.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是現在我們並沒有\N遇到危險跟不自由啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.12,0:06:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是危險而是男人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.62,0:06:11.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不是不自由\N而是非常的不自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.62,0:06:13.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以請妳專心看前面開車嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.49,0:06:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至少在我們閃過\N長群嬰兒車隊的這段時間內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.23,0:06:16.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.66,0:06:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蘭花好厲害喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.83,0:06:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有一個人受傷耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.63,0:06:24.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,閉嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.77,0:06:28.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有個大組織委託我一項工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.61,0:06:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你接受了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.64,0:06:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酬勞不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.78,0:06:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酬勞好到可把這當成最後一次\N然後到某處邊境的行星隱居
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.75,0:06:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.28,0:06:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳要不要一起來？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.05,0:06:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這玩笑太毒了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.65,0:06:44.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.32,0:06:48.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊，不過早點洗手不幹\N也是不錯的計劃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.59,0:06:52.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在我說完你的權利後\N將你銬上手銬的那天來臨前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.83,0:06:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個玩笑也很毒呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.83,0:06:55.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是說真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.80,0:06:57.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.90,0:06:58.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.57,0:07:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,委託人有點…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.51,0:07:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.77,0:07:02.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,託那傢伙的福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.91,0:07:08.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我即使抽一根煙\N也比國中時還要來得緊張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.88,0:07:10.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殺了我的父母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.82,0:07:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把溜出士官學校\N前去報仇的我的一個肺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.35,0:07:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,泡到醫院的甲醛水裡的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.26,0:07:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼那傢伙會找你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.56,0:07:21.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我現在使用假名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.23,0:07:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以他好像沒發現是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.96,0:07:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳覺得如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.10,0:07:26.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是不是該拒絕？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.60,0:07:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不是已經決定了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.17,0:07:31.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我打算接受委託
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.30,0:07:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙的組織規模已經大到\N連軍隊也束手無策
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.77,0:07:39.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事到如今再去跟他抵抗\N然後以愚蠢的死狀出醜，實在是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.94,0:07:42.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你決定那樣做\N就隨你高興吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.28,0:07:43.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.41,0:07:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.92,0:07:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目標是佛特修特倫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.98,0:07:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使是妳也可以嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.16,0:07:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽說店裡剛好沒有客人在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.43,0:07:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真走運呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.66,0:07:58.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.66,0:08:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明明是花店\N賣的卻只有仙人掌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.23,0:08:02.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,實在有點想不通
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.47,0:08:05.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起，只有我被拋出車外\N毫髮無傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.94,0:08:07.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒關係，我已經習慣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.94,0:08:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是距離目的地\N只剩兩條街而已耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.91,0:08:13.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等我們過了這兩條街\N她就沒命了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.71,0:08:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特，把腦袋洗乾淨\N等我來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.68,0:08:17.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳太大意了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.22,0:08:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然大致查過了屋內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.15,0:08:25.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒想到你竟然會用\N這種老套的招數
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.99,0:08:30.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是所謂的"舊皮袋裝新酒"吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.46,0:08:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,士官學校以來的決鬥\N總算可以做個了斷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.97,0:08:39.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,話才說到一半
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.24,0:08:41.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若妳的回答能讓我滿意\N我可以饒妳一命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.14,0:08:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我希望妳一起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.91,0:08:49.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你煩不煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.15,0:08:50.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.58,0:08:53.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,煩人的男人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.45,0:08:55.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惹人嫌…嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.52,0:09:00.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要抽煙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.73,0:09:03.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要遵守規定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.26,0:09:06.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蘭花，都搞定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.33,0:09:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我跟他們說\N我們不是來幫犯人逃獄的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.67,0:09:11.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們都已經了解了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.28,0:09:20.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我下次一定不會再抽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.51,0:09:22.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.45,0:09:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去婉拒工作吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.08,0:09:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只不過是要去拒絕工作的委託
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.52,0:09:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那份見面禮也未免太重了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.39,0:09:32.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敢拒絕那傢伙委託的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.82,0:09:35.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這世上\N我是第一個也是最後一個吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.63,0:09:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.13,0:09:38.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我跟他之間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.36,0:09:41.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一直迴避至今的故事\N終於到了該繼續的時候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.84,0:09:50.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等你回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.84,0:09:52.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再讓你多抽一根吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.65,0:09:55.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,感謝妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.41,0:09:59.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,順便兩個人來喝個通宵如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.52,0:10:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋，事情沒有那麼輕鬆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.55,0:10:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.52,0:10:04.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我走囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.12,0:10:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,門不用鎖\N窗戶幫我關上就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.90,0:10:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.93,0:10:18.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這家寵物店樓上就是目的地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.48,0:10:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是佛特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.75,0:10:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳說什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.68,0:10:33.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後呢，後來怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.15,0:10:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.75,0:10:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少跟我打馬虎眼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.86,0:10:38.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開門見山地說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.46,0:10:39.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是男人跑掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.89,0:10:42.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是敏銳的蘭花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.23,0:10:45.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只顧自己一個人的幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.13,0:10:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是妳理所當然的報應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.16,0:10:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳說的對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.23,0:10:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會洗心革面的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.77,0:10:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.77,0:10:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼我們為了女人的友情\N乾杯之後回家吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.11,0:10:55.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乾杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.61,0:10:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乾杯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.78,0:11:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說到最近的車子\N和男人的沒志氣，實在是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.45,0:11:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思\N你們先回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.42,0:11:09.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.49,0:11:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早點回家吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.96,0:11:13.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特她怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.09,0:11:14.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所謂的好女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.69,0:11:17.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是不輕易死心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.86,0:11:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這真的是最後一根囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.05,0:12:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,告訴我，月亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.15,0:12:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,猴子的耳垂在哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.06,0:12:25.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這真的是個謎題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.30,0:12:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明明已經吃很多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.37,0:12:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過點心卻還吃得下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.37,0:12:38.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是不可思議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.38,0:12:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Bum  Bum  Bum  Bum  Bum  Bum
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.88,0:12:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天堂和降落傘都在天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.59,0:12:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定要對那孩子Kiss\N對未來示出Peace
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.13,0:13:01.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,熱熱鬧鬧的每一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.73,0:13:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,1  2  3
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.77,0:13:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,展開你的雙手  舉起你的單腳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.14,0:13:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,擺出紅鶴的姿勢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.44,0:13:21.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和你一起抱著新鮮的心情\N開心的去摘橘子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.72,0:13:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,PPP  PPP  Happy

